channel.title: Common Problems - v2 suggestions
channel.description:
For those of you that have seen my v1, [font=Verdana][urlhttp://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,195700.0.html]scroll down here[/font], it obviously does not have enough common problems. I'm making menus at the top with drop menus so there isn't a mess of buttons. There'll also be more stuff, but I need suggestions.
I need you people to tell me of common [b]compiling/running[/b] problems [i]not listed[/i] in the first one.
Thanks :)
